{
  "stem": "19690.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it became more and more dangerous for people, non-Jews, to come visit us because she would report everybody.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She was the eye in the sky, as you might say.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And she was always there, always watching.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] as far as other things were, pretty soon-- probably 1938-- the last kosher butcher shop closed.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They emigrated.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And my grandmother wouldn't eat non-kosher meat.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So we started having to have kosher meat shipped from Holland because there were no kosher butcher shops in Mannheim, or Ludwigshafen, or Heidelberg anymore, which were the nearest towns.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And another thing that happened was that no more matzahs were being made in Germany.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I think it was the Passover of 1938-- '39 for sure, but '38, I think, already-- when we had to get matzahs that were made in Poland.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they were imported.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we had to special order them through our synagogue.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And then they would come to us in big boxes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Things became harder and harder.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Also, there were demands that my father and my grandfather give up their business.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And they resisted for a time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And then, in 1938, they finally had to sell the business to some Germans.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And they didn't get much for it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But we had the OK to remain in the house because we owned the house.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They only owned the business.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So my grandfather still had control over the house, and they were getting some interest from rent.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
